title: Beautiful 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms single family home
posting_body: ['REF: 11248762', 'Beautiful 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms single family home with 3 car garage in the extremely desirable and exclusive gated community of Pembroke Falls in the heart of Pembroke Pines.', 'Spacious and functional layout with large loft, fabulous patio and salt water pool perfect for the whole family to enjoy.', 'A spectacular 400 bottle private wine cellar in garage, ample of space throughout, master bedroom downstairs, formal living room, family room, upgraded wood flooring throughout the whole house, large kitchen w/granite countertops, chefs island, AA appliances, and wood cabinets.', 'Great location with mall, restaurants, easy access to expressways, schools, supermarkets and a lot more.', 'VANESSA REID *|* REALTOR', 'COURTESY OF Fortune International Realty']
